  "notes": [
    "This review paper focuses on the viscoelastic properties of biofilms as a quantifiable measure of their structure and composition, and how this relates to their resistance to mechanical and chemical challenges.",
    "The paper establishes connections between biofilm viscoelasticity and antimicrobial penetration, providing a mechanistic basis for treatment strategies.",
    "Multiple infectious diseases are identified as being caused by biofilms, representing a significant clinical burden."
